- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is also likely as the paper tests the proposed method on convolutional neural networks for image classification tasks.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper discusses the performance improvements of the proposed activation function in deep neural networks.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper proposes a new method to improve the performance of neural networks, which is a key area of research in AI.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a less likely category as the paper does not focus on the development of new algorithms or data structures, but rather on the improvement of an existing activation function.
